; Regression test for issue #1114: Error Balancing Multiple Posting Costs in one transaction (BZ#1114)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1114
;
; A transaction with multiple postings each having explicit costs (@) should
; balance correctly. The auto-balance posting should sum all the costs.

2015/01/01 Multiple posting costs
    Assets:Stocks:AAPL   10 AAPL @ $150.00
    Assets:Stocks:GOOG    5 GOOG @ $200.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
              $-2500
             10 AAPL
              5 GOOG  Assets
              $-2500    Cash
             10 AAPL
              5 GOOG    Stocks
             10 AAPL      AAPL
              5 GOOG      GOOG
--------------------
              $-2500
             10 AAPL
              5 GOOG
end test
